title: Local Notes
text:
Local Notes Eagle-Tribune 
Basketball 
The Raider Basketball skills and drills clinic for boys in grades 3-9 will be Oct. 3-4 from 10 a.m.-12 noon and Oct. 17-18 from 2-4 p.m. at Central Catholic. For more information contact Coach Rick Nault at 508-864-2086 or rnault@centralcatholic.net . 
Youth Running 
A Children’s 1.4 mile run/walk for Childhood Obesity will be held Sunday, Oct. 24, at 11;15 a.m. at Lawrence Catholic Academy 101 Parker St. Lawrence. This is a fun, children’s event to help raise funds and awareness for childhood obesity and wellness. The cost is $10 for grades 2 through 8.
